{"article_id":"Ybi7JxpbC2nCa2Jx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The chairman of a House committee","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that recommended a contempt of Congress citation against Attorney General Eric H. Holder Jr. in the Fast and Furious gunrunning probe","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"says","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"there is no evidence so far","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"that White House officials were involved in misleading Congress or engaged in a cover-up .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"And Rep. Darrell E. Issa , California Republican and chairman of the House Oversight and Government Reform Committee , said","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"he hopes","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"the investigation \" stays at Justice \"","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"and the department decides to hand over hundreds of documents","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"it has withheld","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"despite a committee subpoena .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"\" I hope","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"that they don ' t get involved , \"","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Mr. Issa said on \" Fox News Sunday . \"","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"President Obama injected the White House into the Fast and Furious debate last week","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"when he asserted executive privilege over documents","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"still being sought by the committee ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"and the question","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"of whether Mr. Holder will be held in contempt","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"now rests with the full House ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"which is expected to take up the matter this week .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Last week , House Speaker John A. Boehner said","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Mr. Obama ' s action was an \" admission \"","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that \" White House officials were involved in the decision","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"that misled Congress","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and covered up the truth \" about Fast and Furious ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"during which more than 2,000 weapons","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"- including AK-47 semi-automatic rifles","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"were walked to drug smugglers in Mexico .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"But Mr. Issa ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"asked during an appearance on \" Fox News Sunday \"","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"whether lawmakers had any evidence","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that White House officials were involved ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"said ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"\" No , we don ' t . \"","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"The chairman , however , isn ' t backing down on his claim","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"that the Obama administration may have intentionally flooded the Mexican market with Fast and Furious guns","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"to drum up support for gun control .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"emails","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"obtained from the administration","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"show","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"officials knew","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"the incident could help them build a case","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"for banning assault weapons","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"although it ' s unclear whether that motivated them","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"or just realized it after the fact .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"\" Chicken or egg , we don ' t know","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"which came first ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"and we probably never will , \"","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Mr. Issa said on ABC ' s \" This Week. \"","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"\" The people involved saw the benefit","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"of what they were gathering .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Whether that was their original purposes , we ' ll probably never know . \"","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Mr. Issa also said on \" Fox News Sunday \"","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"that he called the mother of slain U.S. Border Patrol agent Brian A. Terry on Saturday night","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"to tell her","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"he ' ll keep digging for the truth about Fast and Furious .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Two weapons","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"found at the scene of the fatal December 2010 shootout with Mexican bandits","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"were purchased by Fast and Furious straw buyers .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"\" I told her","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"that in fact we ' re going to continue ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"regardless of what the vote is this week , \"","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Mr. Issa said .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"\" We have an obligation","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"to get to the bottom of Fast and Furious . \"","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"The investigation into the gunrunning operation kicked into high-gear after the Terry death ,","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"when Sen. Chuck Grassley of Iowa ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"ranking Republican on the Senate Judiciary Committee ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"first challenged the Bureau of Alcohol , Tobacco , Firearms and Explosives-led program .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Several ATF field agents told Mr. Grassley","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"they had serious concerns","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"about weapons","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"being walked into Mexico .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Fast and Furious began in September 2009 with the intent","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"of tracking weapons","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"purchased in gun shops in the Phoenix area","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"to drug cartels in Mexico ,","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"but ATF agents lost track of the weapons .","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"Mr. Obama and Mr. Holder have both denied knowing about Fast and Furious","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"when it began ,","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"but have on numerous occasions likened it to a similar program","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"tried during the administration of President George W. Bush","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"known as \" Wide Receiver . \"","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"Wide Receiver began in 2006","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"and ended in 2007 .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"ATF agents , under what was described as \" controlled delivery , \" allowed the sale and transfer of weapons with assurances from Mexican officials","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"they would be monitored and interdicted in Mexico .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"When many of the weapons were lost","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"after they crossed the border","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"despite being equipped with miniature GPS devices ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"the operation was shut down .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"As a committee chairman , Mr. Issa initiated an investigation into Fast and Furious and a number of hearings on the program .","depth":3},{"id":94,"text":"He predicted a \" bipartisan \" vote in the House this week","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"to hold Mr. Holder in contempt","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"for withholding documents","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"could shed light on who was involved from Justice and the White House .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Rep. Elijah E. Cummings of Maryland , ranking Democrat on the House Oversight and Government Reform Committee , said","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"he is holding out hope","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Mr. Boehner will meet with Mr. Holder","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"to work out an agreement ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"rendering unnecessary the contempt vote","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"set for this week .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"we have a duty to the American public","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"to get those documents , \"","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Mr. Cummings said on \" Fox News Sunday. \" \" I know","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"we can get them.","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"It ' s just a matter of sitting down . \"","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Mr. Cummings said","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"the Justice Department has turned over 7,600 pages of Fast and Furious documents , 1,300 pages of internal deliberative documents","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"and made two dozen department officials available for testimony and interviews before the committee .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"He also said","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Mr. Holder testified nine times before Congress on this issue .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"Mr. Issa blamed Mr. Holder for the failure of negotiations over the documents last week","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"after the two met face-to-face","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"and the attorney general refused to deliver any of the requested records :","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"\" We only broke off negotiations","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"when we got a flat refusal","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"to get the documents","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"we need","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"to continue the investigation . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":247,"left":190,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":137,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":128,"right":136,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":126,"right":127,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":133,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":5,"right":132,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":6,"right":131,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":7,"right":130,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":129,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuc